                <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn">
                   <p>
                      <lb n="1"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> vraḥ vleṅ· svargga
                   </p>
                   <lg n="1" met="upajāti" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<l n="a"><lb n="2"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> Iman divaś śrīmadhurendrasūri<space/>r</l>
<l n="b">agniṁ patantaṁ samakālam atra</l>
<l n="c"><lb n="3"/>śrīvīraśaktyāgamanena so ’ha<space/>m</l>
<l n="d">adrākṣam aṣṭātriśaśāṅkarūpaiḥ <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g></l>
</lg>
                   <lg n="2" met="upajāti" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<l n="a"><lb n="4"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> dr̥ṣṭo mayā dīdhitadiṅmukho ’gni<space/>r</l>
<l n="b">divaḥ patan śrījayavarmmarājye</l>
<l n="c"><lb n="5"/>Atyadbhutaṁ yatsaphalāni manye <space/></l>
<l n="d">jātañ ca netre ca kulañ ca me syuḥ <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g></l>
</lg>
</div>
           <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
                  <app loc="4">
                     <lem>dīdhitadiṅmukho·</lem>
                     <rdg source="bib:Maxwell2009_01">dīpitadiṅmukho</rdg>
                  </app>
                  
               </listApp>         
         </div>
           <div type="translation" source="bib:Maxwell2009_01">
             <p n="1">The Sacred Fire from heaven.</p>
              <p rend="stanza" n="1">I myself, Śrī-Madhurendrasūri, saw this Fire falling from heaven, here, at the time of the arrival of Śrī-Vīraśakti in 1138 <supplied reason="subaudible">Śaka</supplied>.</p>
              <p rend="stanza" n="2">I have seen the Fire lighting up the directions of space <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> falling from heaven into the kingdom of Śrī-Jayavarman - a great wonder, which I believe will entail good results, <supplied reason="subaudible">namely</supplied> high birth, two <supplied reason="subaudible">good</supplied> eyes, and eminent family. May these be mine!</p>
           </div> 
